short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Go from Chessable to Lichess analysis with a single click!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Analyzing positions with Chessable's relatively weak engine can be annoying. Want a stronger engine to analyze with or play against? This extension takes you from Chessable's analysis page to Lichess with a single click. No more copying and pasting FENs, just get straight to analysis and practice!

This extension is affiliated with neither Chessable nor Lichess.
